race.description: Sponsor A Race @ Wenty Dogs Only Ht 2
race.comment: ZIPPING BOTHAM (5) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by one length at this track in a handy 30.05. Awkwardly drawn but likes the trip. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. KIWI HARRY (1) finds it hard to win but has a consistent overall record, having placed 20 of 42 career runs. Filled a minor placings again last time when third (30.06) at this track making it three placings in a row. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from three starts. Expected to feature again. PROCLIVITY (2) is a handy dog who jumped from box 2 last time out and scored by 1.5 lengths at Richmond Straight (17.80). Has a strong record from box 2, including two wins. Expected to feature again. MR. NICKO (3) cannot be ruled out. Something for the Multiples: ON THE LOOSE (6)
